data.description: Lovely and spacious split-level home on hillside with beautiful views of Lake Ewuana, the hills and city lights! Five large bedrooms, nice deck off kitchen for entertaining. Interior has been freshly painted and new carpet installed. Perfect move-in condition. Just 5 minutes from OIT and Sky Lakes Medical Center... Close to everything!
